result.name: Saizeriya

reviews.text: Food is ok, suitable for a group of people or family gathering
Good food great price good service!
Good Italian style chain food restaurant for cheap price. The size of plates is fairly small so if you are hungry I suggest to buy at least 2 dishes. Also the tiramisu is excellent.

Quite good for gathering with friends and families. Usually quite crowded and has to wait during lunch hours. But there are still many good restaurants nearby especially at the rooftop of Tai Yuen Shopping Centre in case you don’t want to queue.
Been here a good few times and tbh their food is clean and taste good. Great prices and good food. Always order multiple dishes cos I’m a fatty :P

result.name: 薩莉亞

reviews.text: 改犑大校力竹翠槐醇輮，他木木，他木殊林杖口氣象局美林來窞殊戈
價錢合理，食物款式足夠，不過好多卡位坐墊都破爛，影響舒適性及觀感。
最入嗰啲枱同埋牆呢就發曬毛跟住就傳出一陣好臭嘅味道
簾价意大利餐食，味道還不錯，性价比高，祇是衛生感覺略差及食客非常多，經常要輪候，今次叫外賣，比較好。
食物一般算好，但衛生環境不佳！應該係管理不善引致
